Author: not_the_cicada
Text: I grabbed a cookie at the holiday party to look all casual and normal, took several nibbles of it, have no idea what it tasted like, and abandoned it on a table while getting coffee.   What the fuck kind of weird person have I become?

Author: bigLlittleL
Text: I took an offered Christmas cookie this week, shoved half of it in my pocket, pretended to take a bite and then spit it in a napkin. Then I sprayed the whole thing with febreeze so I wouldnâ€™t get tempted later on. I am so sick of this disorder and yet- I just keep on doing the same things over and over and over.
